00:02:41.422 --> 00:02:43.026
[both shouting]

00:02:43.426 --> 00:02:44.529
[both groaning]

00:02:44.596 --> 00:02:46.734
Damn you!

00:02:49.071 --> 00:02:50.541
[booming]
[shouting]

00:02:53.213 --> 00:02:54.783
[groans]

00:02:54.850 --> 00:02:55.752
[both gasping]

00:02:58.089 --> 00:02:59.926
[both gasping]
R‐‐Retreat!

00:02:59.993 --> 00:03:01.062
[grunts]

00:03:01.129 --> 00:03:02.398
[gasps]

00:03:02.464 --> 00:03:04.168
‐ Uh‐‐
‐ Let's get moving.

00:03:04.536 --> 00:03:06.439
‐ [Midori] Nakajou.
‐ [gasps]

00:03:06.507 --> 00:03:07.642
Ah!

00:03:08.009 --> 00:03:10.213
Come on, guys!
The shelter is just up ahead!

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:12.619
Everybody, hang in there!

00:03:13.186 --> 00:03:16.359
[distant booming]

00:03:18.063 --> 00:03:19.498
Second Lieutenant, ma'am.

00:03:20.568 --> 00:03:21.904
[Kyouko] What is it?

00:03:21.970 --> 00:03:25.511
Well, would you mind lending
a vehicle out to me?

00:03:26.279 --> 00:03:28.049
Where are you planning
to drive, then?

00:03:28.517 --> 00:03:30.788
Magic Association in Kanto.

00:03:31.557 --> 00:03:33.259
[Katsuto] I'm only
the acting leader.

00:03:33.326 --> 00:03:35.263
I still must fulfill
my responsibilities

00:03:35.330 --> 00:03:37.301
to the master clan conference.

00:03:37.969 --> 00:03:39.305
Yes, I understand.

00:03:39.371 --> 00:03:40.708
Listen up, corporal.

00:03:40.775 --> 00:03:41.877
And sergeant.

00:03:41.944 --> 00:03:43.346
Escort Mr. Juumonji here

00:03:43.413 --> 00:03:45.183
to the Kanto
branch office immediately.

00:03:45.250 --> 00:03:46.419
both: Ma'am!

00:03:54.335 --> 00:03:55.872
[gasps]

00:03:58.611 --> 00:03:59.646
Ah!

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.284
[grunting]

00:04:06.325 --> 00:04:07.762
[rumbling]

00:04:07.829 --> 00:04:08.898
Huh?

00:04:08.964 --> 00:04:10.033
[gasps]

00:04:10.100 --> 00:04:11.703
Everyone down, now!

00:04:12.806 --> 00:04:13.841
[gasps]

00:04:13.908 --> 00:04:15.945
[rumbling]

00:04:22.892 --> 00:04:24.830
[groaning]

00:04:27.535 --> 00:04:28.838
[Midori] Is that...

00:04:29.873 --> 00:04:31.109
[groaning]

00:04:31.175 --> 00:04:32.344
[Midori] Mr. Tsuzura!

00:04:32.411 --> 00:04:34.181
I can't hold it much longer!

00:04:34.248 --> 00:04:35.383
All of you,

00:04:35.450 --> 00:04:37.622
please hurry!
Get to the shelter!

00:04:42.264 --> 00:04:43.233
[gasps]

00:04:43.299 --> 00:04:44.669
[whimpering]

00:04:44.736 --> 00:04:46.005
[Hagane] What are you doing?

00:04:46.072 --> 00:04:47.274
[gasps]

00:04:47.341 --> 00:04:48.677
We've gotta get outta here.

00:04:48.744 --> 00:04:50.447
‐ [Hagane grunts]
‐ [gasps]

00:04:50.515 --> 00:04:51.783
[Hagane] Hurry!

00:04:54.021 --> 00:04:56.459
[exasperated chatter]

00:05:02.872 --> 00:05:05.110
We'll be reaching
the station soon.

00:05:05.177 --> 00:05:07.114
As long as we can get
you all there safely,

00:05:07.181 --> 00:05:08.249
it'll be fine.

00:05:08.316 --> 00:05:09.619
[both gasping]

00:05:13.828 --> 00:05:15.363
[gasps]

00:05:19.706 --> 00:05:20.875
[grunts]

00:05:23.146 --> 00:05:24.448
[all gasping]

00:05:29.726 --> 00:05:34.068
[exasperated chatter]

00:05:34.134 --> 00:05:35.638
‐ [gasps]
‐ What in the‐‐

00:05:35.705 --> 00:05:38.409
So is the underground
shelter intact?

00:05:38.911 --> 00:05:41.382
Nakajou and the others are safe.
[both gasping]

00:05:49.900 --> 00:05:51.335
[both groaning]

00:05:51.904 --> 00:05:54.743
And yet we can't evacuate into
the shelter

00:05:54.809 --> 00:05:56.613
from this entrance anymore,
can we?

00:05:57.682 --> 00:05:59.719
So what will you do now?
[both grunting]

00:06:03.493 --> 00:06:05.565
[Mayumi] I'm going to call
my dad's company.

00:06:05.631 --> 00:06:07.367
They'll be able
to send helicopters

00:06:07.434 --> 00:06:09.238
to evacuate everyone
left behind.

00:06:09.673 --> 00:06:11.543
I'll contact my father, too.

00:06:12.177 --> 00:06:13.446
In that case,

00:06:13.514 --> 00:06:15.383
I'll leave some
of my subordinates with you.

00:06:15.450 --> 00:06:17.120
[Toshikazu] No,
that won't be necessary.

00:06:17.187 --> 00:06:18.089
[all gasping]

00:06:19.458 --> 00:06:21.563
‐ [Kyouko] Inspector.
‐ Ah, Kazu!

00:06:24.101 --> 00:06:25.571
[Toshikazu] Eliminating
external enemies

00:06:25.638 --> 00:06:26.974
is the military's job,

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:29.913
but it's the police's duty
to protect the people.

00:06:30.447 --> 00:06:32.417
So we'll be staying behind.

00:06:32.484 --> 00:06:35.658
Ms. Fujiba‐‐uh,
second lieutenant,

00:06:35.725 --> 00:06:37.595
please rejoin the main unit.

00:06:38.196 --> 00:06:39.599
Right.
I understand.

00:06:40.233 --> 00:06:42.839
Then I leave the rest to you,
Inspector Chiba.

00:06:48.016 --> 00:06:51.188
[Toshikazu] Oh.
How hot is that lady?

00:06:51.255 --> 00:06:52.659
[Erika] In your dreams.

00:06:52.725 --> 00:06:55.163
There's no way you could handle
a woman like that, Kazu.

00:06:55.965 --> 00:06:57.000
[exhales]

00:06:57.067 --> 00:06:58.169
[both chuckling]

00:06:58.236 --> 00:07:00.307
You sure you wanna give
me attitude, Erika?

00:07:00.373 --> 00:07:01.944
[grunts]
Why not?

00:07:02.010 --> 00:07:04.248
‐ [Toshikazu] I did bring you‐‐
‐ [gasps]

00:07:04.315 --> 00:07:06.485
Something I bet you'll think
is pretty awesome.

00:07:06.553 --> 00:07:07.922
[gasps]

00:07:09.158 --> 00:07:10.427
[grunts]

00:07:11.028 --> 00:07:12.030
[exhales]

00:07:17.207 --> 00:07:19.613
[Man] We've lost all contact
with the troop heading

00:07:19.679 --> 00:07:21.984
to the convention center
in heavy vehicle lot

00:07:22.050 --> 00:07:24.321
as well as the vertical tanks
that were on their way

00:07:24.388 --> 00:07:26.359
to secure
the underground shelter.

00:07:27.027 --> 00:07:29.331
Send in the mechanized unit
immediately!

00:07:29.398 --> 00:07:30.534
Yes, sir!

00:07:55.551 --> 00:07:56.653
[lights buzzing]

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:58.791
Hmm.
The flying unit is hidden

00:07:58.857 --> 00:08:00.327
on the inside of your belt.

00:08:00.695 --> 00:08:02.497
[Sanada] It's bulletproof
and resistant to heat,

00:08:02.565 --> 00:08:04.468
electricity,
and bio warfare.

00:08:04.936 --> 00:08:06.707
I've added a basic power
assist function

00:08:06.773 --> 00:08:08.076
like you'd intended.

00:08:08.142 --> 00:08:09.913
[mechanical whirring]

00:08:10.915 --> 00:08:14.054
Well, I can see that it's
an upgrade over my own design.

00:08:14.121 --> 00:08:15.758
I know it's sudden,

00:08:15.825 --> 00:08:17.427
but you'll be joining
Yanagi's unit,

00:08:17.494 --> 00:08:18.797
special officer.

00:08:19.264 --> 00:08:20.668
Yes, sir.
Roger that.

00:08:22.104 --> 00:08:24.241
[mechanical whirring]

00:08:42.745 --> 00:08:45.450
[lens whirring]

00:08:45.518 --> 00:08:49.058
[distant booming]

00:09:01.382 --> 00:09:03.352
[booming]

00:09:03.419 --> 00:09:06.593
[static hissing]

00:09:07.127 --> 00:09:08.831
We've lost the feed
from our unmanned drone

00:09:08.897 --> 00:09:10.433
heading for Hodogaya.

00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:11.703
Huh?

00:09:12.137 --> 00:09:13.574
[Man] We have just
lost communication

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:14.776
with another drone!

00:09:16.078 --> 00:09:17.314
[grunts]

00:09:17.882 --> 00:09:20.253
What the hell is going on here?

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:22.625
[gunshots]
[groaning]

00:09:22.692 --> 00:09:25.831
[distant booming]

00:09:31.743 --> 00:09:33.246
[Shinkuro] Masaki, let's go.

00:09:33.312 --> 00:09:35.016
The bus is leaving.

00:09:35.684 --> 00:09:37.454
No, I'm heading
to the Kanto branch

00:09:37.522 --> 00:09:39.291
of the Magic Association.
‐ [gasps]

00:09:39.358 --> 00:09:41.195
No way!
That's crazy.

00:09:41.262 --> 00:09:42.632
Why would you do that?

00:09:44.903 --> 00:09:46.807
Because
the association magicians

00:09:46.873 --> 00:09:48.644
won't just be standing by.

00:09:49.144 --> 00:09:51.348
I'm sure that they've mustered
a volunteer army

00:09:51.415 --> 00:09:52.585
so I'm going to join up.

00:09:52.652 --> 00:09:53.854
But are you certain?

00:09:55.791 --> 00:09:58.396
I have to because I'm
an Ichijou.

00:09:58.463 --> 00:10:00.366
[gasps]
Masaki.

00:10:02.672 --> 00:10:03.907
<i>[Shinkuro] Have</i>
<i>the others upset you?</i>

00:10:03.974 --> 00:10:05.076
<i>Is that the reason?</i>

00:10:06.145 --> 00:10:07.949
They didn't mean to offend you.

00:10:09.652 --> 00:10:12.157
That kinda thing
doesn't bother me at all.

00:10:12.558 --> 00:10:13.794
In fact,

00:10:13.861 --> 00:10:15.664
the very first time
I went into battle,

00:10:15.731 --> 00:10:17.602
I felt nauseous immediately.

00:10:18.704 --> 00:10:20.908
Although I didn't actually
throw up.

00:10:22.077 --> 00:10:23.146
[grunts]

00:10:25.551 --> 00:10:26.653
‐ [gasps]
‐ [Masaki] It's the Ten

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.358
Master Clan's duty
to protect this country.

00:10:30.059 --> 00:10:33.399
I can't simply ignore
that responsibility.

00:10:33.466 --> 00:10:34.602
After all,

00:10:34.669 --> 00:10:36.640
I'm the Ichijou heir.

00:10:41.883 --> 00:10:43.620
Fine, then!
I'm coming, too!

00:10:43.687 --> 00:10:45.323
I'm your strategist, Masaki!

00:10:45.390 --> 00:10:47.929
If you're going into battle,
then so am I!

00:10:52.572 --> 00:10:55.310
George, I want you to lead
the other students to safety.

00:10:55.376 --> 00:10:56.713
[gasps]

00:10:56.780 --> 00:10:58.917
[Masaki] Because
if you don't go with them...

00:11:00.186 --> 00:11:01.957
I'll be too worried
about their escape

00:11:02.023 --> 00:11:03.426
and unable to focus.

00:11:05.798 --> 00:11:07.133
All right, Masaki.

00:11:07.802 --> 00:11:09.204
You have my word.

00:11:09.271 --> 00:11:11.375
I will make sure
that everybody gets out.

00:11:11.442 --> 00:11:14.281
So you come back safely as well.
You hear me?

00:11:20.326 --> 00:11:22.163
<i>[Shinkurou] You have to,</i>
<i>Crimson Prince.</i>

00:11:22.230 --> 00:11:24.368
<i>Because you're my one</i>
<i>and only commander.</i>

00:11:25.738 --> 00:11:28.844
[indistinct chatter]

00:11:34.054 --> 00:11:36.025
[Suzune] When will
the helicopters get here?

00:11:36.091 --> 00:11:38.597
Hopefully they'll arrive
by 4:30.

00:11:38.664 --> 00:11:40.400
And our should be around
the same time.

00:11:40.466 --> 00:11:42.838
So another 20 minutes, then?

00:11:43.406 --> 00:11:45.578
In addition
to this landing area,

00:11:45.644 --> 00:11:47.247
we'll be keeping
the civilians safe

00:11:47.314 --> 00:11:48.316
until then, right?

00:11:49.318 --> 00:11:50.788
No need to worry.

00:11:51.422 --> 00:11:54.061
<i>[Mayumi] Even if the enemy</i>
<i>should draw near to us,</i>

00:11:54.127 --> 00:11:56.365
<i>our friends will be sure</i>
<i>to drive them out.</i>

00:11:57.868 --> 00:11:59.304
<i>But you guys,</i>

00:11:59.371 --> 00:12:01.275
<i>please don't push yourselves</i>
<i>too hard.</i>

00:12:09.559 --> 00:12:12.965
[distant booming]

00:12:13.767 --> 00:12:16.840
[magical whirring]

00:12:20.413 --> 00:12:21.382
Two.

00:12:21.448 --> 00:12:22.350
[gasps]

00:12:22.417 --> 00:12:23.352
[grunts]

00:12:23.419 --> 00:12:24.388
[grunts]

00:12:29.164 --> 00:12:30.300
[grunts]

00:12:32.170 --> 00:12:33.339
[groans]

00:12:33.406 --> 00:12:34.341
[grunts]

00:12:39.552 --> 00:12:40.721
[grunts]

00:12:40.788 --> 00:12:44.762
[shouting]

00:12:50.608 --> 00:12:53.847
[grunts, shouts]

00:12:55.450 --> 00:12:57.187
[booming]

00:13:01.997 --> 00:13:03.099
Here they come.

00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:04.902
[grunts]

00:13:06.171 --> 00:13:07.407
‐ Attack!
‐ [grunts]

00:13:08.342 --> 00:13:09.277
[shouting]

00:13:10.179 --> 00:13:11.148
[booming]

00:13:11.215 --> 00:13:13.152
[gunfire]
[shouting]

00:13:13.219 --> 00:13:14.221
[shouts]

00:13:16.793 --> 00:13:18.697
[shouting]

00:13:18.764 --> 00:13:20.099
[blow lands]

00:13:22.738 --> 00:13:23.874
[thuds]

00:13:28.482 --> 00:13:29.484
Huh?

00:13:34.027 --> 00:13:35.564
[Yanagi] Special officer.

00:13:36.065 --> 00:13:37.902
We know who the enemy is now.

00:13:39.404 --> 00:13:40.674
[Tatsuya] What?

00:13:40.741 --> 00:13:43.079
[Yanagi] This was installed
in the enemy's armored tank.

00:13:43.145 --> 00:13:44.849
I've confirmed it with Sanada.

00:13:44.916 --> 00:13:47.621
Apparently it's
a sorcery booster.

00:13:47.688 --> 00:13:49.424
A sorcery booster, huh?

00:13:51.195 --> 00:13:53.265
<i>[Tatsuya] One of those</i>
<i>magic amplifier devices</i>

00:13:53.332 --> 00:13:55.436
<i>which was supplied</i>
<i>by the No Head Dragons?</i>

00:13:57.641 --> 00:14:00.179
The enemy's
the Great Asian Alliance, then.

00:14:01.148 --> 00:14:02.918
I am sorry to spring this
on you,

00:14:02.985 --> 00:14:05.289
but there are civilians
in the station plaza

00:14:05.356 --> 00:14:08.029
who have called for helicopters
to get the evacuees out.

00:14:08.630 --> 00:14:10.534
We're going to head
for the station now

00:14:10.601 --> 00:14:12.037
and help in the escape.

00:14:12.738 --> 00:14:13.940
Understood, sir.

00:14:14.509 --> 00:14:16.478
[gunfire]

00:14:16.546 --> 00:14:18.049
[Erika shouting]

00:14:18.917 --> 00:14:20.587
[grunting]

00:14:22.157 --> 00:14:23.627
[Leonhard shouting]

00:14:29.037 --> 00:14:30.641
[helicopter approaching]

00:14:30.708 --> 00:14:32.243
[both gasping]

00:14:32.945 --> 00:14:34.916
[Erika] Rescue choppers
are here!

00:14:35.416 --> 00:14:38.155
Great, so that means our job
will be over soon.

00:14:38.222 --> 00:14:39.491
[Mikihiko] Here comes another!
[both grunting]

00:14:47.708 --> 00:14:49.077
[exhales]

00:14:49.144 --> 00:14:51.115
Looks like we'll be getting out
of here, right?

00:14:52.016 --> 00:14:53.185
[gasps]

00:14:55.958 --> 00:14:57.895
[buzzing]

00:14:58.329 --> 00:14:59.297
[grunts]

00:15:04.141 --> 00:15:05.677
[gasping]
What, chemicals?

00:15:05.811 --> 00:15:06.946
[grunts]

00:15:10.687 --> 00:15:12.390
[buzzing]

00:15:12.457 --> 00:15:14.829
[gasping]

00:15:14.896 --> 00:15:17.635
[whooshing]

00:15:18.302 --> 00:15:19.237
[gasps]

00:15:23.780 --> 00:15:25.216
[Shizuku] Tatsuya.

00:15:27.187 --> 00:15:30.359
[indistinct chatter]

00:15:31.729 --> 00:15:35.136
So who are they, anyway?
Those guys up there?

00:15:36.138 --> 00:15:37.575
Our friends.

00:15:38.375 --> 00:15:39.344
[gasps]

00:15:40.279 --> 00:15:42.083
[Mayumi] Our choppers are here.

00:16:08.737 --> 00:16:09.972
<i>[Tatsuya] She's a riot.</i>

00:16:11.609 --> 00:16:14.949
Miss Mayumi Saegusa
has boarded the helicopter.

00:16:15.449 --> 00:16:17.220
It looks like she'll be
picking up classmates

00:16:17.287 --> 00:16:19.457
and underclassmen
and then withdrawing

00:16:19.525 --> 00:16:20.761
from the area.

00:16:20.828 --> 00:16:22.163
<i>[Yanagi] Roger that.</i>

00:16:22.230 --> 00:16:24.635
<i>After confirming they've left</i>
<i>the combat zone,</i>

00:16:24.702 --> 00:16:26.238
<i>go and rejoin the unit.</i>

00:16:26.305 --> 00:16:27.708
[Tatsuya] Yes, sir.

00:16:28.910 --> 00:16:31.381
[magical whooshing]

00:16:33.954 --> 00:16:35.757
[grunting]

00:16:35.824 --> 00:16:36.759
[gasps]

00:16:40.934 --> 00:16:42.303
Who the heck is that?

00:16:59.739 --> 00:17:00.674
[both gasping]

00:17:01.709 --> 00:17:04.682
[animals snarling]

00:17:06.753 --> 00:17:07.721
[roaring]

00:17:07.788 --> 00:17:08.924
[all shouting]

00:17:08.990 --> 00:17:10.627
[Man] What the hell
are those things?

00:17:14.936 --> 00:17:16.138
Retreat now!

00:17:16.205 --> 00:17:18.610
Fall back and reestablish
our defensive line!

00:17:18.677 --> 00:17:20.112
Go!

00:17:20.179 --> 00:17:21.749
No, don't retreat!

00:17:23.987 --> 00:17:25.289
[all gasping]

00:17:32.170 --> 00:17:35.376
Stir yourselves,
those of you who possess magic!

